OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,Fresidents with disabilities and long-
OL,7,Fterm conditions have split views over
OL,8,Fthe island's .
OL,10,FIt follows a new report from a series
OL,11,Fof government-run group meetings and
OL,12,Finterviews focused on discussing the
OL,13,F'Route 2 - unbearable suffering'
OL,14,Fclause.
OL,16,FWhile some say 'Route 2' brings peace
OL,17,Fof mind and choice, others believe it
OL,18,Fis subjective and the risk of coercion
OL,19,Fis far too high.
