OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FIt was recommended that the Government
OL,7,Fgather disabled islanders' views on
OL,8,F'Route 2' specifically, following
OL,9,Fpublished in November 2023.
OL,11,FThe 'Route 2' category is for those
OL,12,Fwho have been "diagnosed with an
OL,13,Fincurable physical condition that is
OL,14,Fgiving rise to unbearable suffering
OL,15,Fthat cannot be alleviated in a manner
OL,16,Fthe person deems tolerable".
