OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,F'Route 1' is for people with a
OL,7,Fterminal illness who have less than
OL,8,Fsix months to live, or 12 months if
OL,9,Fthey have a neurodegenerative
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FPeople with disabilities and long-term
OL,13,Fhealth conditions, along with their
OL,14,Ffriends, families and carers, were
OL,15,Finvited to share their opinions.
OL,17,FA majority were in favour of 'Route 1'
OL,18,Fwith around a 50-50 split over whether
OL,19,Fthey support 'Route 2'.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
