OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FOne participant said those unbearably
OL,7,Fsuffering without a terminal illness
OL,8,Fare arguably more in need of assisted
OL,9,Fdying.
OL,11,FThey added: "For these people, it's
OL,12,Fpotentially decades of unbearable
OL,13,Fsuffering, not just six months."
OL,15,FAnother said: "This isn't about
OL,16,Fdisability, it's about suffering, and
OL,17,Fchoice for people who feel that they
OL,18,Fcan't go on."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
