OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FHowever, others oppose 'Route 2', one
OL,7,Fsaid: "Route 1 is clear and
OL,8,Fstraightforward, but Route 2 is a
OL,9,Fminefield."
OL,11,FThe risk of coercion was deemed too
OL,12,Fgreat for some.
OL,14,FOne participant stated: "Even if we
OL,15,Fonly get it wrong for 1 or 2 people,
OL,16,Fthat's too many. Too much of a risk."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
