OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FAnother asked: "What happens if one of
OL,7,Fthe doctors or someone outside or
OL,8,Fanyone would say, "Why don't you just
OL,9,Fgo?". The option is there. They all
OL,10,Fwant to see me dead."
OL,12,FChoice, peace of mind and equality
OL,13,Fwere other issues raised by residents.
OL,15,FSome say 'Route 2' gives islanders the
OL,16,Fchoice to end their suffering if they
OL,17,Ffind it unbearable in the future.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
