OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FOne participant said: "I'm in my 80s
OL,7,Fand I'm fine, but who knows what is
OL,8,Fround the corner? I want to discuss
OL,9,Fthis with my children, so they know in
OL,10,Fadvance it's something I may want in
OL,11,Fthe future."
OL,13,FOthers argued that death should not be
OL,14,Fin the hands of individuals to decide.
OL,16,FOne resident stated: "It's playing
OL,17,FGod, it's not for us to choose when
OL,18,Fthe right time is to die."
