OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FSome islanders also expressed that
OL,7,F'Route 2' is a matter of equality,
OL,8,Fstating that people with disabilities
OL,9,Fshould have the same right to die if
OL,10,Fthey are suffering unbearably as those
OL,11,Fwho are terminally ill under 'Route 1'.
OL,13,FOne participant said: "I want a choice
OL,14,Ffor me and my body. Why should that be
OL,15,Fdifferent if I have a disability?"
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
