OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FAnother referenced the high cost of
OL,7,Fcare: "If I'm in pain, incontinent and
OL,8,Fcan't eat, I don't want to be sh*tting
OL,9,Fmy pants day in, day out and it costs
OL,10,Fme #7,000 a month. Why shouldn't I be
OL,11,Fable to choose to go and leave that
OL,12,Fmoney to my children to enjoy?"
OL,14,FPressure and coercion were raised as
OL,15,Fissues by several participants who
OL,16,Fwere worried about how family, friends
OL,17,Fand even health professionals would
OL,18,Fsway someone's view.
