OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FOne resident said: "We have regulation
OL,7,Fand oversight, there's a tiny minority
OL,8,Fof bad eggs like Shipman and but they
OL,9,Fshouldn't dictate the decisions we
OL,10,Fmake. Most professionals are there to
OL,11,Fhelp and support us."
OL,13,FAnother said: "I've certainly
OL,14,Fexperienced doctors with 'compassion
OL,15,Ffatigue', the professionals involved
OL,16,Fwould need to be in the right space
OL,17,Fmentally, to be involved. And to care."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
