OL,3,C'They all want to see me dead':
OL,4,CResidents clash over assisted dying law
OL,6,FAnother participant raised: "We're
OL,7,Fasking for someone else to kill
OL,8,Fsomebody else. What support do they
OL,9,Fget?"
OL,11,FAnother explained: "You see it all the
OL,12,Ftime on the island, fallings out in
OL,13,Ffamilies over money, this would come
OL,14,Finto play here."
OL,16,FPoliticians are expected to debate the
OL,17,Fproposed assisted dying law on Tuesday
OL,18,F21 May.
